Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:30.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ワタシを呼ぶのは誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:35.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}温もりに憧れ行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:37.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}One more time, time, time!
